<br>
Weapon with taunting blow is off of Metal Dragon in PoI.  You have to activate the quest to start him and hes no pansy.<br>
<br>
Junk Beast is doable with 5 people if you have a slower and a good high hp tanks /pointsathimself. He hits for 900s like above and is not to bad.  Blind wears off in 15 or so seconds and just keep taunting and attacking hell stay put like a good puppy.  Hell blind you every minute or so maybe more or less but not much.<br>
<br>
Junk beast drops a nice caster (int only) cloak and a nice priest (wis only) hammer that looks like a mallet. =).  He drops the haste belt but not sure its 34 percent like above, some think its in the high 20s.<br>
<br>
Side note.  The Soldiers in PoI guarding the door dropped a Etheral scroll.  So you can work for these here.  <br>
<br>
Great exp.  So much tinker items and decent gear not to be there exping on your off time.  The mobs are neat to see and refreshing new looks.  The spiders are bad ass looking and remind me of the guy in Terminator2.<br>
<br>
Coinfist Heavyhand<br>
